---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-border mt-20 py-10 bg-base">
  <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-4 grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-sm text-textSecondary">
    <div>
      <img src="/logo.svg" alt="GeorgiaBooked" class="h-6 mb-3" />
      <p class="text-xs text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
        Public records journalism for Georgia. All individuals named are presumed innocent until proven guilty in a court of law.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-textPrimary font-semibold mb-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Explore</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-crimson">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/counties/" class="hover:text-crimson">Counties</a></li>
        <li><a href="/charges/" class="hover:text-crimson">Charges</a></li>
        <li><a href="/search" class="hover:text-crimson">Search</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-textPrimary font-semibold mb-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Editorial</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-crimson">About + Standards</a></li>
        <li><a href="/takedown" class="hover:text-crimson">Takedown Request</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="text-textPrimary font-semibold mb-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Legal</h4>
      <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed">
        Reporting public-record bookings under Ga. Code 50-18-72 (Open Records Act). We publish accurate facts, not opinions. Corrections reviewed within 72 hours.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-4 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-border text-xs text-textMuted flex justify-between">
    <span>© {year} GeorgiaBooked</span>
    <span>An independent Georgia public-records publication.</span>
  </div>
</footer>
